Welcome to our career site and thank you for taking an interest in our great company.
It is fantastic that you have chosen to consider Sage as your next employer, we are a great company with big ambitions that welcomes high performing individuals who want to be part of something truly amazing.
At Sage our colleagues are very important to us, they make us who we are. We have strong values and a high performance culture, where every colleague lives our values of customers first , velocity, do the right thing, innovate and make a difference.
We are passionate about enabling colleagues to be themselves at work and develop a great career. We believe diversity of thought and equal opportunity drives genuine innovation which is why we welcome all qualified applicants and will not discriminate on the grounds of race, color, age, religion, gender, gender identity, sexual orientation, national origin, disability or veteran status.
This site will give you access to our latest vacancies and also give you an insight into what it is like to work at Sage, from colleagues around the world through the "day in the life" videos and our customer stories.
I wish you every success with your application to join Sage.
Sandra Campopiano

Chief People Officer, Sage Group 









