You’ve heard the buzz about cloud solutions. Now get a full understanding of the pros and cons of deploying an enterprise resource planning (ERP) solution in the cloud. Watch this recorded webcast and hear top ERP solution experts discuss these topics: 

Modern ERP software addresses top business drivers that lead to positive ROI.
Choosing the right solution or deployment option can cut costs and complexity.
Deciding factors, including: implementation time, data security/availability, up-front/recurring costs, and much more.


